## n8n@0.89.0 For a comprehensive list of changes, check out the [commits](https://github.com/n8n-io/n8n/compare/n8n@0.88.1...n8n@0.89.0) for this version.
**Release date:** 2020-10-22 - New Nodes - Pushover - Strava - Strava Trigger - Google Translate - Bug Fixes - HTTP Request: Fixed an issue with the POST request method for the 'File' response format - Fixed issue with displaying non-active workflows as active - Fixed an issue related to multiple-webhooks
